    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\ude97 I'm looking to find a new home for my awesome ride! It\u2019s been such a reliable companion and is still in really great shape, both inside and out. It drives super smooth and has plenty of life left for all your upcoming road trips and daily commutes. I've taken really good care of it, and I'm sure you're going to love it as much as I have! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to chat and get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
      "price": 28500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example featuring the high-revving S54 straight-six engine and a tactile 6-speed Getrag manual gearbox. Mechanically robust, it features a documented rear subframe reinforcement and a complete VANOS service, addressing the platform's primary weak points. The throttle response from the individual throttle bodies is sharp, and the limited-slip differential provides excellent power delivery through the corners. While the exterior shows minor road wear consistent with its mileage, the chassis remains stiff and the suspension bushings have been refreshed to maintain factory kinematics. A turn-key performance machine for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle. Mechanically sound. Clean interior. Minor exterior scratches. Title in hand.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 BMW X5 in a stunning Mineral White Metallic finish. This vehicle represents a balanced blend of luxury and utility, currently in solid, dependable condition. The exterior retains a high-gloss shine, though a few minor stone chips on the front fascia reflect its honest road history. Inside, the Mocha Dakota leather interior remains supple and smoke-free; while there is slight wear on the driver\u2019s side bolster, the cabin remains a premium environment. Mechanically, this X5 is sound, backed by a comprehensive service portfolio. It recently underwent a full multi-point inspection, fresh oil service, and the Continental tires show plenty of life. Equipped with the Premium Package, you'll enjoy a panoramic moonroof, 4-zone climate control, and a crisp Harman Kardon surround sound system. It\u2019s a reliable, well-cared-for example ready for its next owner.",
      "price": 32000.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes both reliability and value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure its mechanical systems operate at peak efficiency. The exterior remains distinguished, complemented by a refined interior that reflects diligent ownership. Offering a sophisticated balance of performance and longevity, this vehicle represents a premier investment for those seeking a high-caliber driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a super reliable ride that\u2019s ready for its next adventure? This car has been so good to me and is still in wonderful shape. It\u2019s been well-loved, runs smoothly, and is just waiting for someone new to get behind the wheel. It's perfect for daily commutes or fun weekend getaways. Come take it for a spin and see why I've enjoyed it so much!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 30
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This 2004 BMW M3 (E46) is a mechanically robust example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The 3.2L high-revving inline-six features individual throttle bodies and is mated to a precise 6-speed manual transmission. Critical preventative maintenance is complete, including a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure timing stability. The suspension has been upgraded with Bilstein dampers and refreshed bushings for tightened turn-in and superior damping control. Power is managed through the factory M Variable Differential Lock, providing excellent traction out of corners. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina consistent with a driver\u2019s car, the chassis remains stiff and the engine pulls strongly to its 8,000 RPM redline. The interior maintains its driver-centric ergonomics with well-bolstered Nappa leather seating.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
